---

# Plan миграции RadiaCode iOS → KMP

## Контекст и подход

Приложение хорошо подходит для KMP: чистая архитектура с выраженным слоем доменной логики (70+ UseCase, Repository-интерфейсы, 40+ моделей). Стратегия — **shared-first**: выносим всю бизнес-логику в Kotlin Multiplatform модуль (`shared`), а UI + платформозависимые API остаются нативными (SwiftUI на iOS, Jetpack Compose на Android).

---

## Фазы миграции

### Фаза 0 — Подготовка (1–2 недели)
Не трогаем код. Закладываем инфраструктуру.

| Задача | Детали |
|---|---|
| Создать KMP Gradle проект | `shared/` рядом с `RadiaCode.xcodeproj` |
| Настроить `build.gradle.kts` | targets: `iosArm64`, `iosSimulatorArm64`, `androidTarget` |
| Подключить `shared.xcframework` в iOS target | через SPM или CocoaPods |
| Выбрать Kotlin BLE библиотеку | `Kable` (multiplatform BLE) |
| Выбрать KMP persistence | `SQLDelight` (вместо SwiftData) |
| Выбрать KMP networking | `Ktor` (вместо URLSession) |
| Выбрать KMP DI | `Koin` (вместо FactoryKit) |
| Выбрать реактивность | `kotlinx.coroutines` + `StateFlow` (вместо Combine) |

---

### Фаза 1 — Доменный слой (3–4 недели)

Переносим чистые модели и доменные сущности. Нулевые зависимости от платформы.

#### 1.1 Core Domain Models

```
shared/src/commonMain/kotlin/com/radiacode/domain/model/
```

| Kotlin класс | Из Swift | Ключевые поля |
|---|---|---|
| `RadiationData` | `Model/RadiationData.swift` | `value: Double`, `time: Instant`, `level: SignalizationLevel`, `error: Double?` |
| `RadiationType` | `Model/RadiationType.swift` | enum: `Alpha, Beta, Gamma, XRay` |
| `SignalizationLevel` | `Model/SignalizationAlarmLevel.swift` | enum: `Safe, Low, Medium, High, Critical` |
| `Alarm` | `Model/Alarm.swift` | `level`, `threshold`, `isEnabled` |
| `Settings` | `Model/Settings.swift` | предпочтения пользователя |

#### 1.2 Feature Domain Models

```
shared/src/commonMain/kotlin/com/radiacode/domain/model/
```

**Tracks**
```kotlin
data class Track(
    val id: String,
    val name: String,
    val createdAt: Instant,
    val periods: List<TrackPeriod>,
    val markers: List<TrackMarker>
)

data class TrackMarker(
    val id: String,
    val coordinate: GeoCoordinate,
    val radiationValue: Double,
    val time: Instant,
    val comment: String?
)

data class TrackPeriod(val startTime: Instant, val endTime: Instant?)
data class GeoCoordinate(val lat: Double, val lon: Double, val altitude: Double?)
```

**Spectrum**
```kotlin
data class Spectrum(
    val id: String,
    val name: String,
    val channels: IntArray,        // 1024 каналов
    val calibration: EnergyCalibration,
    val createdAt: Instant,
    val duration: Duration,
    val folder: SpectrumFolder?
)

data class EnergyCalibration(val a0: Double, val a1: Double, val a2: Double)
data class SpectrumFolder(val id: String, val name: String)
```

**Spectrogram**
```kotlin
data class Spectrogram(
    val id: String,
    val name: String,
    val spectra: List<SpectrogramSlice>,
    val createdAt: Instant
)

data class SpectrogramSlice(val time: Instant, val channels: IntArray)
```

**Dose**
```kotlin
data class DoseCounter(
    val id: String,
    val accumulatedDose: Double,  // мкЗв
    val startTime: Instant,
    val excludedIntervals: List<ExcludedInterval>
)

data class ExcludedInterval(val from: Instant, val to: Instant)
```

**Events**
```kotlin
data class RadiationEvent(
    val id: String,
    val time: Instant,
    val value: Double,
    val level: SignalizationLevel,
    val coordinate: GeoCoordinate?
)

enum class EventFilter { All, Alarms, Measurements }
```

**Food Analysis**
```kotlin
data class FoodAnalysis(
    val id: String,
    val product: Product,
    val container: MeasurementContainer,
    val spectrum: Spectrum,
    val result: ActivityCalculationResult?,
    val createdAt: Instant
)

data class ActivityCalculationResult(
    val cs134: Double?,
    val cs137: Double?,
    val totalActivity: Double,
    val isSafe: Boolean
)
```

**Device**
```kotlin
data class BluetoothDevice(val id: String, val name: String, val rssi: Int)
data class DeviceFirmware(val version: String, val buildDate: LocalDate)
data class ConfigurationSettings(/* alarm levels, sensitivity, etc. */)
data class SpectrumSettings(/* accumulation time, reset threshold, etc. */)

sealed class RadiaCodeModel {
    object RC101 : RadiaCodeModel()
    object RC102 : RadiaCodeModel()
    object RC103 : RadiaCodeModel()
    object RC103G : RadiaCodeModel()
    object RC110 : RadiaCodeModel()
    object RCZero : RadiaCodeModel()
    data class RC4xx(val variant: Int) : RadiaCodeModel()
}
```

---

#### 1.3 Repository интерфейсы

Все интерфейсы живут в `commonMain`. Реализации — в платформах.

```
shared/src/commonMain/kotlin/com/radiacode/domain/repository/
```

```kotlin
interface TrackRepository {
    fun observeTracks(): Flow<List<Track>>
    suspend fun getTrack(id: String): Track?
    suspend fun createTrack(name: String): Track
    suspend fun updateTrack(track: Track)
    suspend fun deleteTrack(id: String)
    suspend fun importTrack(data: ByteArray, format: TrackFormat): Track
}

interface TrackMarkerRepository {
    suspend fun createMarker(trackId: String, marker: TrackMarker): TrackMarker
    suspend fun updateMarker(marker: TrackMarker)
    suspend fun deleteMarker(id: String)
    suspend fun fetchMarkers(trackId: String): List<TrackMarker>
}

interface SpectrumRepository {
    fun observeSpectra(): Flow<List<Spectrum>>
    suspend fun getSpectrum(id: String): Spectrum?
    suspend fun saveSpectrum(spectrum: Spectrum)
    suspend fun deleteSpectrum(id: String)
    suspend fun updateCalibration(id: String, calibration: EnergyCalibration)
}

interface SpectrumFolderRepository {
    fun observeFolders(): Flow<List<SpectrumFolder>>
    suspend fun createFolder(name: String): SpectrumFolder
    suspend fun deleteFolder(id: String)
}

interface SpectrogramRepository {
    fun observeSpectrograms(): Flow<List<Spectrogram>>
    suspend fun saveSpectrogram(spectrogram: Spectrogram)
    suspend fun deleteSpectrogram(id: String)
    suspend fun importSpectrogram(data: ByteArray): Spectrogram
}

interface DoseCounterRepository {
    fun observeDoseCounter(): Flow<DoseCounter>
    suspend fun saveDoseCounter(counter: DoseCounter)
    suspend fun resetDose()
}

interface ExcludedIntervalsRepository {
    fun observeIntervals(): Flow<List<ExcludedInterval>>
    suspend fun addInterval(interval: ExcludedInterval)
    suspend fun removeInterval(id: String)
}

interface EventsRepository {
    fun observeEvents(filter: EventFilter): Flow<List<RadiationEvent>>
    suspend fun getEvents(from: Instant, to: Instant): List<RadiationEvent>
    suspend fun clearEvents()
}

interface FoodAnalysisRepository {
    fun observeAnalyses(): Flow<List<FoodAnalysis>>
    suspend fun getAnalysis(id: String): FoodAnalysis?
    suspend fun saveAnalysis(analysis: FoodAnalysis)
    suspend fun deleteAnalysis(id: String)
}

interface DataBufferRepository {
    fun observeRadiationData(): Flow<RadiationData>
    fun observeActivityData(): Flow<Double>
    suspend fun getHistory(from: Instant, to: Instant): List<RadiationData>
}

interface ConfigurationRepository {
    fun observeConfiguration(): Flow<ConfigurationSettings>
    suspend fun updateConfiguration(settings: ConfigurationSettings)
}
```

---

#### 1.4 Device интерфейсы

```
shared/src/commonMain/kotlin/com/radiacode/domain/device/
```

```kotlin
interface BluetoothScanner {
    fun observeDevices(): Flow<List<BluetoothDevice>>
    fun startScan()
    fun stopScan()
}

interface DeviceConnection {
    val connectionState: StateFlow<ConnectionState>
    suspend fun connect(device: BluetoothDevice)
    suspend fun disconnect()
    suspend fun sendCommand(command: DeviceCommand): DeviceResponse
    fun observeDataStream(): Flow<DeviceFrame>
}

sealed class ConnectionState {
    object Disconnected : ConnectionState()
    data class Connecting(val device: BluetoothDevice) : ConnectionState()
    data class Connected(val device: BluetoothDevice) : ConnectionState()
    data class Error(val cause: Throwable) : ConnectionState()
}
```

---

### Фаза 2 — BLE Protocol Codec (2–3 недели)

Самая ценная часть — кодирование/декодирование бинарного протокола RadiaCode. **Полностью платформонезависимо**, переносится 1:1 из Swift в Kotlin.

```
shared/src/commonMain/kotlin/com/radiacode/ble/codec/
```

#### Структура

```kotlin
// BluetoothCommand.kt
sealed class DeviceCommand {
    abstract fun encode(): ByteArray
}

sealed class DeviceResponse {
    abstract class Parser<T : DeviceResponse> {
        abstract fun parse(data: ByteArray): T
    }
}

// Команды потока данных
class DataBufferCommand : DeviceCommand() {
    override fun encode(): ByteArray { ... }

    data class Response(
        val eventId: EventId,
        val groupId: GroupId,
        val channelId: ChannelId,
        val flags: Flags,
        val values: List<Double>
    ) : DeviceResponse()

    enum class EventId { /* из DataBufferCommand.Model.EventId */ }
    enum class GroupId { /* из DataBufferCommand.Model.GroupId */ }
}

// Команды спектра
object SpectrumCommand : DeviceCommand()
object SpectrumResetCommand : DeviceCommand()
data class EnergyCalibrationCommand(val calibration: EnergyCalibration) : DeviceCommand()

// Прошивка
object FirmwareGetVersionCommand : DeviceCommand()
data class FirmwareImageWriteCommand(val data: ByteArray, val offset: Int) : DeviceCommand()

// Системные
object SettingsCommand : DeviceCommand()
data class ConfigurationCommand(val settings: ConfigurationSettings) : DeviceCommand()
object DeviceTimeCommand : DeviceCommand()
object SetLocalTimeCommand : DeviceCommand()
data class PlaySignalCommand(val signal: SignalType) : DeviceCommand()
object DoseResetCommand : DeviceCommand()
```

#### Парсинг бинарного формата

```kotlin
// shared/src/commonMain/kotlin/com/radiacode/ble/codec/DataParser.kt
object DataParser {
    fun parseFrameValue(bytes: ByteArray): RadiationData { ... }
    fun parseSpectrum(bytes: ByteArray): IntArray { ... }
    fun parseCalibration(bytes: ByteArray): EnergyCalibration { ... }
    fun parseFirmwareVersion(bytes: ByteArray): DeviceFirmware { ... }
    fun parseConfiguration(bytes: ByteArray): ConfigurationSettings { ... }
}
```

---

### Фаза 3 — Use Cases (2–3 недели)

```
shared/src/commonMain/kotlin/com/radiacode/domain/usecase/
```

Use Cases не знают о платформе — только зависят от Repository-интерфейсов.

```kotlin
// Track
class TrackCreateUseCase(private val repo: TrackRepository) {
    suspend operator fun invoke(name: String): Track = repo.createTrack(name)
}

class TrackImportUseCase(private val repo: TrackRepository, private val parser: TrackFormatParser) {
    suspend operator fun invoke(data: ByteArray, format: TrackFormat): Result<Track>
}

class TrackMergeUseCase(private val repo: TrackRepository) {
    suspend operator fun invoke(source: Track, target: Track): Track
}

// Spectrum
class SpectrumSaveUseCase(private val repo: SpectrumRepository)
class SpectrumUpdateCoefficientsUseCase(private val repo: SpectrumRepository)
class SpectrumCreateFolderUseCase(private val repo: SpectrumFolderRepository)

// Dose
class DoseCounterFetchUseCase(private val repo: DoseCounterRepository) {
    fun invoke(): Flow<DoseCounter>
}

class DoseCounterSaveUseCase(private val repo: DoseCounterRepository)
class DoseBackgroundLevelUseCase(private val repo: DoseCounterRepository)

// Events
class EventsUseCase(private val repo: EventsRepository) {
    fun invoke(filter: EventFilter): Flow<List<RadiationEvent>>
}

class ActiveAlarmUseCase(private val dataBuffer: DataBufferRepository, private val config: ConfigurationRepository) {
    fun invoke(): Flow<Alarm?>
}

// Device
class FirmwareUpdateUseCase(private val connection: DeviceConnection, private val networkService: FirmwareNetworkService) {
    suspend operator fun invoke(): Flow<FirmwareUpdateProgress>
}

// Food Analysis
class ActiveFoodAnalysisUseCase(private val repo: FoodAnalysisRepository)
class FoodActivityCalculationUseCase(private val spectrumAnalyzer: IsotopeActivityCalculator)
```

---

### Фаза 4 — Сервисы бизнес-логики (3–4 недели)

```
shared/src/commonMain/kotlin/com/radiacode/domain/service/
```

Эти сервисы содержат чистые вычисления — идеальные кандидаты для KMP:

```kotlin
// Пересчёт доз
class DoseBarCalculator {
    fun buildBars(samples: List<DoseSample>, intervals: List<ExcludedInterval>): List<DoseBar>
}

class DoseIntervalsBuilder {
    fun build(counter: DoseCounter): List<DoseInterval>
}

class DoseSampleManager {
    fun addSample(dose: Double, time: Instant)
    fun getAggregated(from: Instant, to: Instant): List<DoseSample>
}

// Обработка спектра
class SpectrumPulseConverter {
    fun toCps(channels: IntArray, calibration: EnergyCalibration, duration: Duration): List<SpectrumPoint>
}

class IsotopeActivityCalculator {
    fun calculate(spectrum: Spectrum, product: Product, container: MeasurementContainer): ActivityCalculationResult
}

// Построение данных для графиков
class RadiationChartBuilder {
    fun buildHardnessChart(data: List<RadiationData>): List<HardnessPoint>
    fun buildRateChart(data: List<RadiationData>, window: Duration): List<RatePoint>
}

class SpectrogramChartBuilder {
    fun build(spectrogram: Spectrogram): SpectrogramChartModel
}

// Сигнализация
class AlarmEvaluator {
    fun evaluate(current: Double, levels: List<Alarm>): SignalizationLevel
}

// Аналитика событий
class EventsGrouper {
    fun group(events: List<RadiationEvent>, filter: EventFilter): List<EventGroup>
}
```

---

### Фаза 5 — Networking (1–2 недели)

Заменяем URLSession на Ktor.

```
shared/src/commonMain/kotlin/com/radiacode/data/network/
```

```kotlin
// Интерфейс сетевого сервиса
interface FirmwareNetworkService {
    suspend fun getLatestFirmware(model: RadiaCodeModel): FirmwareDTO
    suspend fun downloadFirmware(url: String): ByteArray
}

interface AuthNetworkService {
    suspend fun refreshToken(token: String): AuthToken
}

// Ktor реализация
internal class KtorNetworkEngine(
    private val client: HttpClient
) {
    // interceptors → Ktor плагины: Auth, Retry, Logging
}
```

---

### Фаза 6 — Persistence: SQLDelight (4–5 недель)

Это самая трудоёмкая фаза. 10 версий схемы SwiftData → SQLDelight с миграциями.

```
shared/src/commonMain/sqldelight/com/radiacode/
```

**SQLDelight схемы** (`.sq` файлы):

```sql
-- FrameValue.sq
CREATE TABLE frame_value (
    id TEXT PRIMARY KEY,
    value REAL NOT NULL,
    time INTEGER NOT NULL,      -- Unix timestamp ms
    latitude REAL,
    longitude REAL
);

-- Track.sq
CREATE TABLE track (
    id TEXT PRIMARY KEY,
    name TEXT NOT NULL,
    created_at INTEGER NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE track_marker (
    id TEXT PRIMARY KEY,
    track_id TEXT NOT NULL REFERENCES track(id) ON DELETE CASCADE,
    latitude REAL NOT NULL,
    longitude REAL NOT NULL,
    value REAL NOT NULL,
    time INTEGER NOT NULL,
    comment TEXT
);

-- Spectrum.sq
CREATE TABLE spectrum (
    id TEXT PRIMARY KEY,
    name TEXT NOT NULL,
    channels BLOB NOT NULL,     -- IntArray serialized
    calibration_a0 REAL NOT NULL,
    calibration_a1 REAL NOT NULL,
    calibration_a2 REAL NOT NULL,
    duration_ms INTEGER NOT NULL,
    created_at INTEGER NOT NULL,
    folder_id TEXT REFERENCES spectrum_folder(id)
);

-- DoseCounter.sq
CREATE TABLE dose_counter (
    id TEXT PRIMARY KEY,
    accumulated REAL NOT NULL,
    start_time INTEGER NOT NULL
);

-- ... и т.д. для Spectrogram, Event, FoodAnalysis
```

**Репозитории (SQLDelight impl)**:
```kotlin
class SQLDelightTrackRepository(private val db: RadiacodeDatabase) : TrackRepository {
    override fun observeTracks(): Flow<List<Track>> =
        db.trackQueries.selectAll().asFlow().mapToList().map { it.map(::toDomain) }
    // ...
}
```

**Миграция данных iOS → Android**: экспорт через существующий `BackupExportManager` (JSON) → импорт в SQLDelight. Схема миграции уже реализована на iOS.

---

### Фаза 7 — DI через Koin (1 неделя)

```kotlin
// shared/src/commonMain/kotlin/com/radiacode/di/SharedModule.kt
val sharedModule = module {
    // Repositories
    single<TrackRepository> { SQLDelightTrackRepository(get()) }
    single<SpectrumRepository> { SQLDelightSpectrumRepository(get()) }
    single<DoseCounterRepository> { SQLDelightDoseRepository(get()) }
    // ... остальные репозитории

    // Use Cases
    factory { TrackCreateUseCase(get()) }
    factory { TrackImportUseCase(get(), get()) }
    factory { SpectrumSaveUseCase(get()) }
    factory { DoseCounterFetchUseCase(get()) }
    factory { EventsUseCase(get()) }
    factory { FirmwareUpdateUseCase(get(), get()) }

    // Services
    single { DoseBarCalculator() }
    single { SpectrumPulseConverter() }
    single { IsotopeActivityCalculator() }
    single { AlarmEvaluator() }

    // Network
    single { KtorNetworkEngine(get()) }
    single<FirmwareNetworkService> { KtorFirmwareService(get()) }
}

// iOS-специфичный модуль (в iosMain)
val iosBluetoothModule = module {
    single<BluetoothScanner> { CoreBluetoothScanner() }
    single<DeviceConnection> { CoreBluetoothConnection() }
}

// Android-специфичный модуль (в androidMain)
val androidBluetoothModule = module {
    single<BluetoothScanner> { KableBluetoothScanner() }
    single<DeviceConnection> { KableDeviceConnection() }
}
```

---

### Фаза 8 — iOS интеграция (2–3 недели)

После фаз 1–7 iOS остаётся на SwiftUI. ViewModels постепенно начинают использовать Kotlin Use Cases через `shared.xcframework`.

**Паттерн — ObservableObject-обёртка над Kotlin Flow:**
```swift
// iOS: адаптер для Kotlin StateFlow
@Observable
final class TrackListViewModel {
    private let useCase: TrackCreateUseCase  // из shared.xcframework
    private let repository: TrackRepository  // Kotlin интерфейс

    var tracks: [Track] = []

    func onAppear() {
        // Kotlin Flow → Swift AsyncSequence через KMP-NativeCoroutines
        Task {
            for await tracks in repository.observeTracks() {
                self.tracks = tracks
            }
        }
    }
}
```

Рекомендуемая библиотека для Flow → Swift: **[KMP-NativeCoroutines](https://github.com/rickclephas/KMP-NativeCoroutines)** (делает Kotlin Flow совместимым с Swift `async/await` и Combine).

---

## Итоговая структура проекта

```
radiacode/
├── RadiaCode.xcodeproj             # iOS (SwiftUI, CoreBluetooth, SwiftData)
├── shared/                         # KMP модуль
│   ├── build.gradle.kts
│   └── src/
│       ├── commonMain/kotlin/com/radiacode/
│       │   ├── domain/
│       │   │   ├── model/          # Фаза 1: 40+ data class
│       │   │   ├── repository/     # Фаза 1: 12 интерфейсов
│       │   │   ├── device/         # Фаза 1: BLE интерфейсы
│       │   │   ├── usecase/        # Фаза 3: 30+ UseCase
│       │   │   └── service/        # Фаза 4: чистые вычисления
│       │   ├── ble/codec/          # Фаза 2: бинарный протокол
│       │   ├── data/
│       │   │   ├── network/        # Фаза 5: Ktor
│       │   │   └── db/             # Фаза 6: SQLDelight
│       │   └── di/                 # Фаза 7: Koin
│       ├── iosMain/kotlin/         # CoreBluetooth адаптер
│       └── androidMain/kotlin/     # Kable BLE адаптер
└── androidApp/                     # Android (Jetpack Compose) — Фаза 8+
```

---

## Ключевые риски и решения

| Риск | Решение |
|---|---|
| SwiftData → SQLDelight (10 версий схемы) | Перенести через JSON-экспорт, написать миграторы в commonMain |
| Combine → Coroutines/Flow | KMP-NativeCoroutines для iOS-стороны |
| CoreBluetooth → Kable | `BluetoothScanner`/`DeviceConnection` интерфейсы изолируют BLE-слой |
| Числовая точность (Float32 в RadiaCode) | Явно использовать `Double` в KMP, проверить совпадение с текущим Swift кодом |
| Бинарный протокол (Protocol.pdf) | Codecы из фазы 2 — самое ценное, переносить с unit-тестами |
| FactoryKit DI → Koin | Прямой аналог, миграция механическая |
| WatchOS / Widgets | Остаются на Swift навсегда, подключаются к shared через Koin iOS модуль |

---

## Приоритет фаз

```
Фаза 1 (Domain Models + Interfaces)    ← начать здесь, нет рисков
Фаза 2 (BLE Codec)                     ← высокая ценность, легко тестировать
Фаза 3 (Use Cases)                     ← чистый Kotlin, без платформенных зависимостей
Фаза 4 (Services)                      ← числовые алгоритмы, критично покрыть тестами
Фаза 5 (Networking)                    ← Ktor хорошо документирован
Фаза 6 (SQLDelight)                    ← самое трудоёмкое, делать последним
Фаза 7 (DI)                            ← финальная склейка
Фаза 8 (iOS интеграция)                ← постепенно заменяем Swift сервисы на Kotlin
```

Общая оценка: **6–8 месяцев** для полного `shared` модуля с покрытием тестами. Без Android UI (только shared + iOS) — около 4 месяцев.

content.content:
//
//  SettingsComposer.swift
//  Radiacode
//
//  Created by Pavel Marinchenko on 16.07.2023.
//

import Foundation
import Combine

protocol SettingComposerInfoProtocol {

    func isEnabled(setting: SettingsModel) async -> Bool
}

protocol SettingComposerDataProtocol {

    func set(settings: [UInt32: UInt32]) async

    func set(raw setting: UInt32, value: UInt32) async

    func set(setting: SettingsModel, value: UInt32) async

    func get(setting: SettingsModel) async -> UInt32

    func update(setting: SettingsModel, to value: Bool) async
}

actor SettingComposer {

    private typealias DeviceControl = SettingsModel.DeviceControl
    private typealias SoundControl = SettingsModel.SoundControl
    private typealias VibrationControl = SettingsModel.VibrationControl

    // MARK: Notifications
    let settingsChangedSubject = PassthroughSubject<SettingComposerInfoProtocol, Never>()

    // MARK: Init

    private var settings: [UInt32: UInt32] = [:]
}

extension SettingComposer: SettingComposerInfoProtocol {

    func isEnabled(setting: SettingsModel) async -> Bool {
        guard let state = settings[setting.command] else {
            return false
        }

        switch setting {
        case .device(.vibration):
            return (state & DeviceControl.vibration.value) > 0

        case .device(.sound):
            return (state & DeviceControl.sound.value) > 0

        case .device(.leds):
            return (state & DeviceControl.leds.value) > 0

        case .device(.power):
            return (state & DeviceControl.power.value) > 0

        case .sound(.clickers):
            return (state & SoundControl.clickers.value) > 0

        case .sound(.alarm):
            return (state & SoundControl.alarmMask) != 0

        case .vibro(.alarm):
            return (state & VibrationControl.alarmMask) != 0

        default:
            return false
        }
    }
}

extension SettingComposer: SettingComposerDataProtocol {

    func set(settings: [UInt32: UInt32]) async {
        self.settings = settings
        settingsChangedSubject.send(self)
    }

    func set(raw setting: UInt32, value: UInt32) async {
        self.settings[setting] = value
        settingsChangedSubject.send(self)
    }

    func set(setting: SettingsModel, value: UInt32) async {
        self.settings[setting.command] = value
        settingsChangedSubject.send(self)
    }

    func get(setting: SettingsModel) async -> UInt32 {
        self.settings[setting.command] ?? 0
    }

    func update(setting: SettingsModel, to enabled: Bool) async {
        guard var state = self.settings[setting.command] else {
            return
        }

        switch setting {
        case .device(let type):

            let value: UInt32

            switch type {
            case .vibration:
                value = DeviceControl.vibration.value
            case .leds:
